00:01:06,336 --> 00:01:10,778
=The Truth=

2
00:01:11,531 --> 00:01:14,136
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:17,710 --> 00:01:19,669
Jiang Lianhong, take a look.

4
00:01:21,270 --> 00:01:22,669
I said she looked like...

5
00:01:24,350 --> 00:01:25,270
He Jie.

6
00:01:26,029 --> 00:01:26,669
You mean

7
00:01:26,669 --> 00:01:28,669
the He Jie you raped 20 years ago?

8
00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:32,470
What's He Jie's

9
00:01:32,589 --> 00:01:34,270
connection to Jiang Honghai?

10
00:01:36,589 --> 00:01:38,270
I've told you everything I know.

11
00:01:38,270 --> 00:01:39,029
Go arrest him.

12
00:01:39,029 --> 00:01:40,669
Why do you keep questioning me?

13
00:01:45,750 --> 00:01:47,070
