to protect Chen Xiaomeng.

75
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:09,389
Let's head back.

76
00:05:09,389 --> 00:05:11,070
Captain Leng might have new leads.

77
00:05:12,149 --> 00:05:13,230
Let's go. I'll drive.

78
00:05:19,509 --> 00:05:20,310
Let's go.

79
00:05:41,949 --> 00:05:42,589
Captain Leng.

80
00:05:44,670 --> 00:05:45,349
We got something.

81
00:05:46,029 --> 00:05:48,070
Jiang Han, 40 years old,
no prior record.

82
00:05:48,230 --> 00:05:49,589
He also grew up in the village.

83
00:05:49,589 --> 00:05:51,550
He's around the same age
as Jiang Lianhong.

84
00:05:51,550 --> 00:05:53,269
He teaches at a mason training school

85
00:05:53,349 --> 00:05:55,190
and helps young villagers find work.

86
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:57,349
Bring Jiang Han in immediately.

87
00:05:57,949 --> 00:05:59,349
See if we can get

88
00:05:59,349 --> 00:06:00,589
new leads from him.

89
00:06:00,829 --> 00:06:02,750
Focus on finding Jiang Honghai.

90
00:06:02,949 --> 00:06:04,070
Yes, sir. I'm on it.

91
00:06:05,131 --> 00:06:07,864
(Ye Qian: Chen Xiaomeng is safe.)

92
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:12,990
