on construction sites.

109
00:06:55,829 --> 00:06:56,949
Who was that person?

110
00:06:57,509 --> 00:06:58,310
Jiang Honghai.

111
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,990
His family used to be
in the renovation business.

112
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,750
They're pretty well-off.

113
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,509
His dad used to be a village official.

114
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:06,110
Most of the fishponds

115
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:07,589
in our village belong to his family.

116
00:07:08,589 --> 00:07:09,149
Right.

117
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,430
Honghai has this habit.

118
00:07:10,949 --> 00:07:12,990
He loves making soup
with live brood fish.

119
00:07:13,469 --> 00:07:14,349
Says it's nourishing.

120
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:15,990
He has it every single day.

121
00:07:16,349 --> 00:07:18,550
So, he always keeps
a fish tank where he lives.

122
00:07:19,269 --> 00:07:20,509
Every few days,

123
00:07:20,990 --> 00:07:23,230
he has his family
deliver fresh brood fish to him.

124
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:24,949
You may not know.

125
00:07:25,389 --> 00:07:26,709
Brood fish are really expensive.

126
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,829
Luckily, his family has fishponds.

127
00:07:29,589 --> 00:07:31,550
Or who could've afforded that?

128
00:07:32,331 --> 00:07:32,990
(Yunxi Police)

129
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:34,310
On May 25th,

130
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:36,430
where were you
between 10 PM and midnight?

131
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:38,750
May 25th?

132
00:07:39,149 --> 00:07:39,949
