133
00:07:41,349 --> 00:07:43,430
That night,
I was drinking at a restaurant.

134
00:07:44,149 --> 00:07:45,750
Who were you drinking with?

135
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:48,670
Jiang Lianhong and Jiang Honghai.

136
00:07:49,029 --> 00:07:50,790
But Jiang Honghai can't hold his liquor.

137
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:53,190
He was clamoring to leave before 11 PM.

138
00:07:53,349 --> 00:07:55,149
I drank for a bit longer
and then left too.

139
00:07:55,149 --> 00:07:56,829
Didn't pay attention to the exact time.

140
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:59,589
Did you see Jiang Honghai again
after that?

141
00:08:00,029 --> 00:08:00,750
No.

142
00:08:02,149 --> 00:08:03,670
Besides home and construction sites,

143
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:04,550
does Jiang Honghai

144
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:05,750
have any other places to stay?

145
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:09,469
Jiang Honghai is a strange one.

146
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:11,070
He's used to keeping to himself.

147
00:08:12,389 --> 00:08:15,269
But I have a storage warehouse.

148
00:08:15,949 --> 00:08:17,630
A year ago, he asked me for its key

149
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:19,630
and wanted to keep
construction equipment there.

150
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:21,430
He hasn't returned the key yet.

151
00:08:21,670 --> 00:08:23,389
Where is that warehouse?

152
00:08:23,949 --> 00:08:25,469
28, North Xinyuan Lane.

153
00:08:25,670 --> 00:08:27,389
In the abandoned place
by the noodle shop.

154
00:08:40,310 --> 00:08:41,109
We got something.

155
00:08:41,829 --> 00:08:43,829
Jiang Honghai also drank
with them that night.

156
00:08:43,829 --> 00:08:44,709
And he left first.

157
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:45,629
Wang Tong,

158
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:46,872
share the address.

159
00:08:46,872 --> 00:08:47,430
Yes.

160
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:47,989
Let's go.

161
00:09:12,749 --> 00:09:13,510
Master,

162
00:09:14,190 --> 00:09:15,510
